sentences: Yoon Bo-ra (born December 30, 1989), better known by the mononym Bora, is a South Korean singer and actress.
Bora was born on December 30, 1989, in Seoul.
section: == Early life and education ==

sentences: She majored in Musical Theater in Myongji University, and graduated in February 2015.
